This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques for facial recognition. The paper also involves the use of 3D models (MM) and graphics (GR) to generate facial UV maps. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential applications of their research in human-computer interaction (HC). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.MM, cs.GR, and cs.HC.
